				<td colspan="2"><span>I have npc mark, npc health, inspect buffs, and am finishing LP #4 in saving for 6 ( which will probably be used for Spell Awareness ) anyways my questions are.
<br />

<br />
1. Health of Target's Target - Can anyone give a detailed comment about what they actually see when they use this, and why they would even use it.
<br />

<br />
2. Health Regeneration - Is it 1 point per ability level or more ? 
<br />

<br />
I do nothing except LDoN and I am almost always the group leader so the leadership points fall like rain, in normal adventure, I'm the puller, slower, mezer,and haster so designateing an MA isn't a huge deal for me. It would be cool if the hp regen is more than 1 hps to break 30 hps standing regen out of sheer boredom<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
Caligarien Songsinger
<br />
Level 65 Bard
