				<td colspan="2"><span>Target of Target pops up an additional window that will basically just show you the health of your Target's Target.
<br />

<br />
It is actually kind of nice.  Healers <i>love</i> it because they don't have to ask what % the mob is at when tageting the MA.  Other people may find it interresting to keep an eye on the MA's health while they attack the mob.  And the MA loves it because they will immediately know if they've lost agro (the mob will be Targeting someone else).</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
