				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: L Abilities: 2 Questions <a name="31270"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 29 04 3:03 AM</span></td>
